    • Method Detail

      • isInNewClaimWizardDraftSave

        public static boolean isInNewClaimWizardDraftSave()
        Returns if the current commit is happening in the context of an intermediate draft save of the NewClaimWizard. This can be used to customize behavior in rules fired during a draft save commit if required.
        Returns:
        boolean - the value of the flag

      • isInNewClaimWizardFinalSave

        public static boolean isInNewClaimWizardFinalSave()
        Returns if the current commit is happening in the context of the final save of the NewClaimWizard during the finish step. This can be used to customize behavior in rules fired during the final save commit if required.
        Returns:
        boolean - the value of the flag

      • shouldSaveInAB

        public static boolean shouldSaveInAB(Contact contact)
        Deprecated. since 8.0.1 - this API is no longer supported use isInNewClaimWizardFinalSave to determine if the code is running in the context of the NewClaimWizard's final save
        Returns false
        Parameters:
        contact - the contact to save in AB
